#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/49/
msgid "Quilboar - Rally"
msgstr "野猪人 - 进击"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/49/
msgid "Scale your bloodgems using an early [[Sanguine Refiner||122566]]. Then, [[Razorfen Vineweaver||122562]] casts 3 or more permanent gems on itself each fight, while [[Bloodsnout Warlord||122564]] casts an insane amount of temporary gems on your board. You also want to shield as many Quilboars as possible using [[Hog Watcher||122737]]. In the endgame, you may gem transfer using [[Gem Confiscation||110642]] onto a [[Corrupted Bristler||120033]] to double the effectiveness of your blood gems."
msgstr "在早期使用 [[Sanguine Refiner||122566]] 来成长鲜血宝石。然后 [[Razorfen Vineweaver||122562]] 在每次攻击都会为自己使用 3 个或更多的永久宝石，而[[Bloodsnout Warlord||122564]] 则会在你的棋盘上疯狂地施放大量的临时宝石。你还要用 [[Hog Watcher||122737]] 尽可能多地为野猪人套上圣盾。在终局中，你可以使用 [[Gem Confiscation||110642]] 将宝石转移到 [[Corrupted Bristler||120033]] 上，使你的鲜血宝石效果翻倍。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/49/
msgid "Gem Scaling ([[Sanguine Refiner||122566]]) + Payoff ([[Razorfen Vineweaver||122562]]/[[Bloodsnout Warlord||122564]])"
msgstr "鲜血宝石成长 ([[Sanguine Refiner||122566]]) + 贴宝石 ([[Razorfen Vineweaver||122562]]/[[Bloodsnout Warlord||122564]])"

